document_data.name: Yavendel
document_data.mainbody: 'Yavendel''' ({{Pronounce|YAW|ven|del|refs={{Cite adventurers league/City of Danger|40}}}}) was a [[druid]] of the [[Emerald Enclave]] in [[Mulmaster]].
document_data.History: In [[1491 DR]], Yavendel found some of her burrowing mammal friends acting strange. Investigating, she discovered that they had escaped into a tunnel inside the city. Following them inside, Yavendel exited in the [[Oxpit Tavern]], where she met an adventuring party hired to locate some vandals.
document_data.Activities: In 1491 DR, Yavendel patrolled just outside the city at the behest of the Emerald Enclave.
